data.description: This is the home you have been waiting for....spotless and move in ready.  Situated on over an acre of land just north of Wewahitchka , this 3BR/2BA home features an open living area, master suite with soaking tub, large kitchen and dining area.  Exterior features include storage shed, pole barn, outdoor kitchen area, and a tree house for the kids. Must see to appreciate all this property has to offer.
